Insider Activity


Individual




Bradley T. Sheares



Dr. Bradley T. Sheares is Independent Director at Henry Schein, Inc., Independent Director at Honeywell International, Inc., and Independent Director at Progressive Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Iroko Pharmaceuticals LLC, Iroko Pharmaceuticals, Inc., Henry Schein, Inc., Honeywell International, Inc., and Progressive Corp.
Dr. Sheares was previously employed as Independent Director by Covance, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Reliant Pharmaceuticals LLC, President by Merck Human Health US, and President-Human Health Division by Merck & Co., Inc. He also served on the board at IMS Health, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Fisk University and a doctorate degree from Purdue University.



